.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH tapectl-report 1  "tapectl-report " 
.SH NAME
tapectl\-report \- Generate reports
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBtapectl report\fR [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-y\fR|\fB\-\-yes\fR] [\fB\-\-config\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate reports
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Output in JSON format
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Show what would be done without making changes
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Enable verbose output
.TP
\fB\-y\fR, \fB\-\-yes\fR
Skip confirmation prompts
.TP
\fB\-\-config\fR \fI<CONFIG>\fR
Path to config file
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
tapectl\-report\-summary(1)
Overview: units, tapes, tenants, capacity
.TP
tapectl\-report\-fire\-risk(1)
Units at risk: below min copies/locations
.TP
tapectl\-report\-copies(1)
Copy count distribution per unit
.TP
tapectl\-report\-tape\-only(1)
Tape\-only unit status
.TP
tapectl\-report\-dirty(1)
Units with changes since last snapshot
.TP
tapectl\-report\-pending(1)
Staged data pending write
.TP
tapectl\-report\-verify\-status(1)
Verification recency
.TP
tapectl\-report\-health(1)
Drive error trends
.TP
tapectl\-report\-capacity(1)
Volume capacity utilization
.TP
tapectl\-report\-age(1)
Snapshot age distribution
.TP
tapectl\-report\-events(1)
Audit trail browsing
.TP
tapectl\-report\-compaction\-candidates(1)
Volumes flagged for compaction
.TP
tapectl\-report\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
